map.legendDescription: Domestic protein supply (grams per person per day)

title: Domestic protein supply, grams per person per day
subtitle: Total protein domestic supply from crops, measured in average daily per capita terms (grams per person per day). These values represent crop supply after correction for trade (imports, exports & stocks), but prior to crop allocation for alternative uses such as animal feed and industrial processes.
